\emph on
direct method
\emph default
 up to samples width of 
\begin_inset Formula $10$
\end_inset

 seconds.
 This figure also shows a very good agreement between the standard deviation
 based on Reference [10] (black cross points) and based on the set of generated
 signals.
 Once again lets recall that all these signals contains the same 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

amount of knowledge
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 (i.e.
 sames histories, detections, etc.).
